WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en-US

00:00:07.160 --> 00:00:14.160
When choosing the beef short ribs, select parts with more fat which will add more flavour and aroma to the bean sprouts

00:00:16.540 --> 00:00:20.700
Wash the bean sprouts and then spread on the bottom of the plate

00:00:22.220 --> 00:00:30.880
Mix the beef diced garlic, sliced chillies, and all of the seasoning together evenly

00:01:16.200 --> 00:01:20.120
put the beef pieces into bow and  mix well

00:01:24.560 --> 00:01:27.440
spread out on top of the bean sprouts

00:01:30.880 --> 00:01:35.720
Add 1/3 cup of water to the outer pot of the electric rice steamer, put in the plate with the ingredients

00:01:51.820 --> 00:01:58.780
press the switch and steam for around 5 minutes until cooked,

00:02:10.740 --> 00:02:14.680
sprinkle on the crispy fried shallots

